title: Boys and Girls Soccer: Details and results from 10/1
text:
MORE Senior Ed Seaman scored off a through ball from sophomore Lou Nazzaro in the second overtime period leading Brick Memorial to a 2-1 victory over Southern on Thursday afternoon.
Erik Fatovic scored the first goal of the game for the Mustangs off an assist from Ed Seaman in the 15th minute.
Brick Memorialâ€™s Joe Zahlamann recorded nine saves in the win for the Mustangs.
Anthony Delagarza finished with five saves for the Rams.
